  "text": "Due to its attractive features, many new backscatter communication systems have been developed and introduced recently. In this section, we first review emerging RFID systems with tag-to-tag communication capability which are similar to bistatic systems. Then, the integration of backscatter communications with wireless-powered communication networks (WPCNs) [CITATION_1] is discussed. Finally, RF-powered backscatter cognitive radio networks (CRNs), i.e., an integration of RF-powered CRNs and ABCSs are reviewed.",
